    "notes": "property_names: scalar/list fields (use setProperty / object.get with @Property). reference_names: use setReference. Optional reference_target_types: reference slot -> allowed Wwise object type(s) for setReference value. Source tables: wwiseobject_*.html for 2025.1.x. Content verified against 2025.1.6_9117 (Audiokinetic redirects 2025.1.x patch URLs to latest patch).",
    "changes_from_2023_1_17": [
      "AttenuationDistanceScaling added to all voice and bus objects",
      "GameAuxSendDSF added to all voice and bus objects (dual-shelf filter for game-defined aux sends)",
      "OutputBusDualshelf added to all voice and bus objects (dual-shelf filter on output bus route)",
      "GlobalOrPerObject renamed to GlobalOrPerObjectScope in RandomSequenceContainer",
      "ActorMixer removed from official 2025.1.x WAAPI object reference docs"
    ]
  },
